  <data key="d3">17.0</data>
  <data key="d4">"The prefrontal cortex is critically involved in empathetic capacities, particularly the higher cognitive aspects, and its decline reduces empathy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The prefrontal cortex is crucial for empathy; its impairment results in diminished understanding of others' emotions and intentions."</data>
