  <data key="d3">9.0</data>
  <data key="d4">"The prefrontal cortex is the necessary brain structure that supports and maintains the fragile 'layer of civilization'—our social norms and morality."</data>
  <data key="d5">"foundation, supports structure"</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-b3da432a99878091a368929c8cf97145</data>
</edge>
